piskorski.util.arraylist

Class StringArrayList

  • java.lang.Object
    • piskorski.util.arraylist.StringArrayList

  • public final class StringArrayList
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is an efficient implementation of string array lists. The functionality of some operations is limited due to efficiency reasons.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      StringArrayList()
      Constructs an empty boolean-list with an initial capacity of ten.
